    # "I drive over and pick Kendra up."
    "Conduzco hasta allí y recojo a Kendra."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:24
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_63ac34de:

    # "As soon as I park the car, she jumps into the passenger seat."
    "En cuanto aparco el coche, se sube al asiento del copiloto."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:31
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/kendra_whoa.wav'
    voice 'voices/kendra_whoa.wav'

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:32
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_cbfbb13b:

    # sg "Woah, you're wearing a suit. So fancy! You look like a fucking stud!"
    sg "¡Vaya, llevas traje! ¡Qué elegante! ¡Pareces un puto semental!"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:33
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_93be84d9:

    # pc "Thanks! You look amazing too."
    pc "¡Gracias! Tú también estás increíble."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:34
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_f9a9256b:

    # sg "Yeah, I got all dressed up and shit. No big. Let's go eat!"
    sg "Sí, me he arreglado y todo eso. No es nada. ¡Vamos a comer!"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:36
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_eddccec4:

    # sg "I'm so hungry! Let's eat!"
    sg "¡Tengo tanta hambre! ¡Vamos a comer!"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:40
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_92e5e80f:

    # "We drive to The Grotto and are led to a table by the host."
    "Conducimos hasta The Grotto y el maître nos lleva a una mesa."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:45
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_2e543208:

    # "We sit at our table and begin looking over the menus."
    "Nos sentamos y empezamos a mirar los menús."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:46
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_5508ff55:

    # sg "Wow this place is so fancy. Is the food here any good?"
    sg "Vaya, este sitio es muy elegante. ¿La comida aquí está buena?"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:47
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_494fc97b:

    # pc "Yeah, it's amazing."
    pc "Sí, está increíble."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:48
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_f3f82f77:

    # sg "That's good. Whenever my parents took me to fancy restaurants like this, the food would always end up looking super pretty, but tasting gross."
    sg "Qué bien. Cada vez que mis padres me llevaban a restaurantes elegantes como este, la comida siempre acababa teniendo un aspecto súper bonito, pero sabía fatal."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:49
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_720f2b03:

    # sg "Like they want to put some weird spices on it or something to make it different from other places, but I just want some dang chicken nuggets, you know?"
    sg "Como si quisieran echarle especias raras o algo así para que sea diferente de otros sitios, pero yo solo quiero unos malditos nuggets de pollo, ¿sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:50
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_039e7c94:

    # pc "Ha, you order whatever you'd like."
    pc "Ja, pide lo que quieras."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:56
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_45ee2ac4:

    # "A couple of minutes later the server approaches us to take our order."
    "Unos minutos más tarde, el camarero se acerca a nosotros para tomar nota."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:57
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_477af30d:

    # "Server" "Are you ready to place your order, or would you like some more time to look over the menu? I can answer any questions you have."
    "Server" "¿Están listos para pedir o quieren un poco más de tiempo para mirar el menú? Puedo responder a cualquier pregunta que tengan."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:58
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_11cbd844:

    # sg "Do y'all have any chicken nuggets?"
    sg "¿Tienen nuggets de pollo?"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:59
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_2e8784f2:

    # "Server" "We have pan-fried buttermilk and panko chicken breast medallions, served over shingled potatoes with a creamy thyme sauce."
    "Server" "Tenemos medallones de pechuga de pollo fritos en sarten con suero de leche y panko, servidos sobre patatas en láminas con una salsa cremosa de tomillo."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:60
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_e04bae2d:

    # sg "Is that kinda like chicken nuggets?"
    sg "¿Eso es algo parecido a los nuggets de pollo?"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:61
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_b16a388e:

    # "Server" "Yes ma'am. It's like chicken nuggets."
    "Server" "Sí, señora. Es como los nuggets de pollo."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:62
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_f57e52c6:

    # sg "Gimme some of them then. And a Dr. Pepper."
    sg "Pues ponme unos de esos. Y un Dr. Pepper."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:65
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_3d97b32c:

    # "After the server takes our orders, Kendra and I chat for a while."
    "Después de que el camarero nos toma nota, Kendra y yo charlamos un rato."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:68
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_55bc048d:

    # "After we talk for a while, our food is brought out."
    "Tras hablar un rato, nos traen la comida."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:72
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_12bdb83d:

    # sg "I don't think these people know what chicken nuggets are."
    sg "No creo que esta gente sepa lo que son los nuggets de pollo."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:75
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_84073847:

    # sg "Oh well. I'm hungry. I'll give it a try."
    sg "Bueno, da igual. Tengo hambre. Los probaré."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:78
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_bfde7d54:

    # "We continue chatting and eating."
    "Seguimos charlando y comiendo."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:88
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_35489cf9:

    # "When the waiter brings the bill out, Kendra quickly snatches it up."
    "Cuando el camarero trae la cuenta, Kendra la agarra rápidamente."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:89
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_618f396f:

    # sg "Wait, these chicken nuggets were thirty bucks!?"
    sg "¡Espera, ¿estos nuggets de pollo costaban treinta dólares!?"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:90
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_4853a04c:

    # sg "That's crazy! They were good, but I could get like 200 nuggies from McDonalds for that price."
    sg "¡Es una locura! Estaban buenos, pero por ese precio podría comprar como 200 nuggets en McDonald's."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:91
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_011e7134:

    # pc "You're paying for the atmosphere here too. Can't get a view like this at McDonalds."
    pc "Aquí también pagas por el ambiente. En McDonald's no tienes unas vistas como estas."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:92
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_5895d784:

    # sg "Yeah I guess. But dang, thirty dollars?"
    sg "Sí, supongo. Pero, joder, ¿treinta dólares?"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:93
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_7ceb71ac:

    # pc "Don't worry about that. I got it."
    pc "No te preocupes por eso. Yo me encargo."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:94
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_738449bb:

    # sg "If you say so. Just know, you don't have to take me anywhere fancy and expensive. I'd be just as happy anywhere else with you."
    sg "Si tú lo dices. Pero que sepas que no tienes que llevarme a ningún sitio elegante y caro. Sería igual de feliz en cualquier otro sitio contigo."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:100
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_99c80cd6:

    # "After I pay, we start to walk out and stop to look over the lake for a moment."
    "Después de pagar, empezamos a salir y nos detenemos un momento para contemplar el lago."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:101
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_a1d66bdf:

    # sg "It {i}is{/i} really pretty though."
    sg "La verdad es que {i}es{/i} muy bonito."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:110
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_cd966f27:

    # "I lean in and kiss her. She returns the kiss passionately, pressing hard into my mouth, her hands climbing up my body."
    "Me inclino y la beso. Ella me devuelve el beso apasionadamente, presionando con fuerza contra mi boca, mientras sus manos suben por mi cuerpo."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:111
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_f0046ea4:

    # pc "Do you want to dance?"
    pc "¿Quieres bailar?"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:112
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_3f909766:

    # sg "Not really. I want you to take me back to your place and pound me into your bed."
    sg "La verdad es que no. Quiero que me lleves a tu casa y me folles en tu cama."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:113
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_1909f58c:

    # pc "That sounds good too."
    pc "Eso también suena bien."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:120
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_72295199:

    # "We leave, then drive back to my house and rush up to my bedroom, barely able to keep our hands off each other."
    "Nos vamos, volvemos a mi casa y subimos corriendo a mi habitación, sin poder quitarnos las manos de encima."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:127
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_72295199_1:

    # "We leave, then drive back to my house and rush up to my bedroom, barely able to keep our hands off each other."
    "Nos vamos, volvemos a mi casa y subimos corriendo a mi habitación, sin poder quitarnos las manos de encima."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendragrottodate.rpy:130
translate spanish kendragrottostartdate_60db26d1:

    # "We go get in the car, then I drive her back to her house and tell her goodnight."
    "Nos subimos al coche, la llevo de vuelta a su casa y le doy las buenas noches."

